narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Broader understanding of several climate economics topics
Deepened my understanding on the issue of climate change from many aspects that I have never thought of.

narratives.question_text: How well did the knowledge, skills, and insights gained in this class align with your expectations?
What are the strengths and weaknesses of the course and how could it be improved?
comments: It's very well organized and rich in content. Papers we've discussed are generally very representative of a certain topic. I hope the discussions could be deeper and summaries of competing research could be possibly provided.
Liked the flexibility but almost too much. More guidelines on the presentation would have been helpful.
I truly enjoyed the presentation on the selected topic and I believe students can engage better if students can do more than one presentation during the semester.

narratives.question_text: What advice would you give to a student considering taking this class?
comments: Better participate more in class and join the discussion with the professor and classmates.
